orever release, waive, discharge and covenant not to sue Belightful Yoga, LLC for any injury or death caused by their negligence or other acts. 8. Furthermore, I give permission to Belightful Yoga, LLC to use photographs and/or comments in which I or family members have or are featured. Photographs and/or testimonials obtained during a Belightful Yoga, LLC sponsored event may be shared with program participants, and/or used as a part of a public display which may include the Belightful Yoga, LLC website and/or print and electronic publications. 9. I understand all classes/series are non-refundable and non-transferable. 10. Payment of Services: Students must provide full payment prior to participation in class. 11. Returned Checks: All returned checks will be charged a $35.00 processing fee.</p>

<p><strong><em>I acknowledge that I have read this document in its entirety or, if I am unable to read the form, it has been read to me in its entirety.  I have had an opportunity to ask questions, which have been answered to my
satisfaction.  I voluntarily consent to the terms and conditions stated above.
</em></strong></p>


<% unless waiver.object.non_user.present? && waiver.object.non_user.age < 18 %>
<div class="row">
	<div class="col-md-8"><label class="waiver-value"><%= @waiver.signature %></label><br>
		<%= waiver.label :signature, "Signature" %></div>
	<div class="col-md-4"><label class="underline" style="width:225px;"><%= Date.today.strftime("%m/%d/%Y")%></label><br>
		<label>Date</label></div>
</div>

<br><br>
<% end %>

<% unless @waiver.guardian_of.blank? %>
<div class="row">
	<div class="col-md-12"><%= waiver.label :guardian_of, raw("<u>If Under 18 Years of Age:</u> As parent/legal
guardian of") %><label class="waiver-value"><%= @waiver.guardian_of %></label><br>
	<label>
I consent to the above terms and conditions.</label></div>	
</div>

<div class="row">
	<div class="col-md-8"><label class="waiver-value"><%= @waiver.guardian_signature %></label><br>
		<%= waiver.label :guardian_signature, "Signature of Parent" %></div>
	<div class="col-md-4"><label class="underline" style="width:225px;"><%= Date.today.strftime("%m/%d/%Y")%></label><br>
		<label>Date</label></div>
</div>
<% end %>

</div>
<% end %>